{"tid":650353,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馬國明背心穎咀詩詠：唔使交代","createTime":"2018-05-02T08:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T11:10:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7a083f5a193160b7a26b125623a012b19b94ec","tid":650353,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T08:57:10.000Z","msg":"馬國明日前趁女友黃心穎與家人旅行，偷啜契妹唐詩詠，更直言唔使交代！至於身在外地的心穎就晒三點式反擊，更被家姐心妙將其正面的泳裝照放上社交網。<br />\n<br />\n藝人馬國明與郭晉安昨日現身火炭為無綫新劇《白色強人》拍攝外景，二人大熱天時分別穿上整套西裝及皮褸，頻呼好熱！馬國明透露最近都在拍攝手術室戲，直言覺得複雜，而5月中會到深圳拍外景，他更自爆日前與契妹、劇中女友唐詩詠拍咀戲，被笑指趁正印女友黃心穎去旅行才拍親熱戲，他說：「又唔係我安排嘅。（同心穎備案？）做嘢唔使同佢交代啦！」<br />\n<br />\n出手遮事業線<br />\n雖然詩詠是其契妹，但拍攝時並沒尷尬，更指二人合作多次，今次是第二次咀對方。談到心穎在社交網上載穿比堅尼的背面照，馬國明說：「冇睇呀！（有傳正面照畀你？）唔知喎！睇吓手機先，拍緊嘢未得閒！」另外，心穎的家姐心妙將心穎的正面泳衣照放上網，但就巧妙地用手遮實心穎的事業線。<br />\n<br />\n郭晉安仔女探班<br />\n郭晉安相隔多年再與馬國明合作，大讚對方變得成熟。談到拍劇會否少了時間陪仔女？他透露仔女曾到內地探班：「之前拍《再創世紀》有到內地探班，個仔就讚啲外景飯盒好食，個女就讚我拍劇造型好靚仔！」又指暑假會與太太歐倩怡帶小朋友去旅行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/H9b._epnP9oT4FlvG9R1gQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/57830b484f7c29334699ff0d3a28133b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FH9b._epnP9oT4FlvG9R1gQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F57830b484f7c29334699ff0d3a28133b&h=7245ce24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%8E%E8%83%8C%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8E%E5%92%80%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%A0-%E5%94%94%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3-214500876.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%25A9%258E%25E5%2592%2580%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E8%25A9%25A0-%25E5%2594%2594%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E4%25BB%25A3-214500876.html&d=ep6YnHRG0cyB7Oss7hYNUiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a7e769b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%8E%E8%83%8C%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8E%E5%92%80%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%A0-%E5%94%94%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3-214500876.html</a>"},{"pid":"8fea064b0e6928fe03ef126da14d4dff982dab60","tid":650353,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T09:40:09.000Z","msg":"說好的背心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458be2e758b6f25c9b458ccb1068bf792f7ba97a","tid":650353,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T10:00:32.000Z","msg":"背心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19b9c9dcba4bfc789aeb7ca030e390033f1dbc2","tid":650353,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"又唐詩詠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3f78fb6afd0a625132e070b5272878283abc86","tid":650353,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T10:11:38.000Z","msg":"背心仔呢"},{"pid":"bc3756ce6a827afb80b277fcbbd98111fde7e90b","tid":650353,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"真男人洗咩交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62beee1e26f7e583beba484a5ceda454ea6589e3","tid":650353,"uid":7001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"諗到馬明咀到唐姨個嘴就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有棟仁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5022a203b4a81e53edde7b05e7153a183e18cba0","tid":650353,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T11:10:08.000Z","msg":"屌點解會見到隻煩膠港女"}]}